ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: would be great if you are truly interested in Japan.
I strongly recommend to others since they will be able not only to get skills in discussion but also in writing appropriate papers in social science.
I would recommend those people who are interested in Japan's foreign policy and politics.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: gave me a comprehensive survey of Japan in both political and economic fields.
I improved my ability to write papers on social science, especially political science, which greatly helped me to finish my final papers on the other social science classes.
This class allows me to think about Japan's policy and history from the perspective of political science.
